After 3 weeks of preparation, Hae-Joon and another crew member dive underwater to work on part of the platform. While performing their work, her partner sinks into the abyss due to an equipment failure. When Hae-Joon gets back on the platform more crew members start to die off in mysterious ways.
What they soon learn is that an underwater monster has come aboard the oil rig platform and is feeding off the crew members. Hae-Joon and her co-workers must now fight for their very lives, while Captain Jung-Man holds the key to the monster's reappearance ...

